        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Methamphetamine Response Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill designates methamphetamine as an emerging drug threat (a new and growing trend in the use of an illicit drug or class of drug). It also directs the Office of National Drug Control Policy to implement a methamphetamine response plan.</p>]]>
        </text>
